en.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ki%E1%BA%BFm-M%C3%B4n/poem-FOVq1DqoCC5TOmWRvb9bAQ">Kiếm Môn - 劍門</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BB%99-xu%C3%A2n-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Nh%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%C3%A2y-t%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ABm-th%E1%BA%A3o-%E1%BB%91c-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-nr_c_lQJykhIJf-dB-zXww">Mộ xuân đề Nhương Tây tân nhẫm thảo ốc kỳ 4 - 暮春題瀼西新賃草屋其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/T%E1%BB%A9-t%E1%BB%AD-Hoan-h%E1%BB%99i-th%C3%AD-tr%C3%BAng-ph%C3%B3-b%E1%BA%A3ng/poem-xRbuuoTSWkEL4ivSEJfXSQ">Tứ tử Hoan hội thí trúng phó bảng - 賜子懽會試中副榜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/V%C3%A3n-t%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-c%C3%B4ng/poem-cDElVqf2JwRbA8T7Kf-a_A">Vãn tư đồ công - 輓司徒公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/author-KitWPFSrhqgQGR4JMcSBew">Nguyễn Ức</a>)<br></div>	</div>
